gr-osmosdr is a GNU Radio block for interfacing with various radio hardware.
While primarily being developed for the OsmoSDR hardware, this block also
supports:

 - FUNcube Dongle
 - FUNcube Dongle Pro+
 - sysmocom OsmoSDR Devices
 - RTL2832U based DVB-T dongles
 - RTL-TCP spectrum server
 - MSi2500 based DVB-T dongles
 - SDRplay RSP
 - gnuradio .cfile input
 - RFSPACE SDR-IQ, SDR-IP, NetSDR (incl. X2 option)
 - AirSpy Wideband Receiver
 - CCCamp 2015 rad1o Badge
 - Great Scott Gadgets HackRF
 - Nuand LLC bladeRF
 - Ettus USRP Devices
 - Fairwaves UmTRX
 - Red Pitaya SDR transceiver
 - FreeSRP
